author: andygumbrecht
msg: Changed serialVersionUIDs in 'org.apache.openejb.math' that conflict with identical commons.math classes (from which they are copied). Not serious, but intellij, netbeans and possibly other IDEs see these classes as the same and can lead to incorrect imports.
Would it maybe be better to remove the 'org.apache.openejb.math' namespace and pull in a dep on commons.math?
